<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6399740>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Families Luciferidae and Sergestidae. A) Belzebub faxoni (Borradaile, 1915) (CCDB 5930). B) Lucifer typus H. Milne-Edwards, 1837 (CCDB 5904). C) Acetes americanus americanus Ortmann, 1893 (CCDB 5931). D) Peisos petrunkevitchi Burkenroad, 1945 (CCDB 5932). Animals from Brazil, São Paulo, R/V Soloncy Moura Expedition, st. 3 (A), st. 6 (B), Ubatuba (C, D). Sex: male (A, B), female (C, D). Scale bars (mm): A—2, B—2; C—5; D—8. Photographs by R.C. Buranelli." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6399740/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

